      "content": "it’s not even about changing circumstances anymore. it feels more permanent than that. like there's nothing left inside to actually change. if the person i was is actually gone, then what am i even doing here? i'm just taking up space that i don't deserve. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life.",
